    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is a driver-focused 2011 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to deliver linear power up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed manual transmission and delivered to the rear wheels through an M Variable Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes reinforced rod bearings and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and induction systems remain robust. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and shows minimal bushing deflection. While the exterior reflects its status as a well-maintained driver's car, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain razor-sharp.",
