      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained luxury SUV that strikes the perfect balance between sophistication and daily utility. The exterior features a deep metallic finish that still catches the light beautifully, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear bumper consistent with careful use. Inside, you\u2019ll find an impeccably clean, smoke-free cabin appointed with premium leather upholstery. While there is light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, the interior remains plush and supportive. Mechanically, this vehicle is in excellent health; it comes with a comprehensive service history, including a recent full synthetic oil change and a cooling system flush. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake pads were replaced within the last 5,000 miles. All electronic features\u2014from the panoramic sunroof and heated seats to the high-fidelity sound system\u2014function exactly as intended. This is a reliable, well-cared-for vehicle that offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
